channel.title: Wierd java problem... please help me!

for 2 days ago my java stop worikng and whan it was stop working i was take a "System time reset" and reset it to the day before... and then it was working agine, but the same thing happend now... it wont work (i live in norway and the cloack is 00:50 here now) and before midnight it was working and i dont wanna take a system time reset agine... so what is wrong i havent done anything.
please help me, u can help me on TeamViewer if needed. thanks for answers and sorry for bad spelling (Cauze Norwegian :D)

javac is not recognized as an internal or external command, executable program or batch file. Press any key to continue ...[/code]
